description.p:
In the plastic formed article of the present invention, it is desired that:
(1) The element M is Si;
(2) The organometal vapor deposited layer has a thickness in a range of 3 to 40 nm;
(3) The plastic substrate is formed by using a biodegradable plastic material and, particularly, a polyhydroxyalkanoate such as polylactic acid; and
(4) The plastic substrate is a bottle, and the vapor deposited film is formed on at least an inner surface of the bottle.
